name ninecolors
category Package
revision 76924
shortdesc Select colors with proper WCAG color contrast
longdesc This package carefully selects and defines 9 colors for 13 hues
longdesc each. All colors with the same suffix number have equal
longdesc luminance level. Also the color black is of level 0, and the
longdesc color white is of level 10. By simply choosing two colors in
longdesc the above list, which differ in level by at least 5, as
longdesc foreground and background colors, you will get proper WCAG
longdesc Color Contrast.
